{"tid":761380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖冇片有劇本]地鐵港女大戰廢佬","createTime":"2018-07-30T10:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T12:45:10.000Z","uid":131884,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b0f546104ef24c4ccbf3f5f2eced8019320b44","tid":761380,"uid":131884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:48:58.000Z","msg":"就咁既<br />\n岩先尖沙咀站往荃灣上車，<br />\n有個後生妹就坐左係到，前面企左個阿伯。架車就迫到佐敦站D人都逼唔到上車。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =後生妹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =阿伯<br />\n.....=聽唔清，可能冇講野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：阿伯，你XX(聽唔清)掂左我隻腳好多次喔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：冇事既，唔洗驚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咩唔洗驚，我點知你係咪搏我懞？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：(笑一笑，安靜左陣)<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n路人：(咁好心你就讓個位比阿伯啦。)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔洗，我就落車<br />\n路人：(細路女你又唔係唔舒服)<br />\n....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁我大肚係咪要話你知啊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：哦你大肚啊，咁唔好意思囉<br />\n......<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：.....我都79歲囉......冇，只係隻腳有D唔舒服姐.....都冇著數攞<br />\n然後我就落車了<br />\n件事有四個真相<br />\n架車真係逼<br />\n廢佬真係老<br />\n後生妹真係後生 二字頭 皮膚非常好 而且眼大大[冇圖]<br />\n大肚真係唔覺<br />\n全程冇粗口，廢佬頗有禮貌<br />\n路人圍屌後生女<br />\n<br />\n眾法官點睇，應該判邊個贏?<br />\n<br />\n廢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後生妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951efd565a8940574a434bf353e86c5cf6a92144","tid":761380,"uid":27247,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:20:26.000Z","msg":"淨係知路人最撚柒"},{"pid":"be86cf75e89d1c00da8371937488889067d84e75","tid":761380,"uid":37447,"like